---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="bg-espresso text-bone mt-32">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-10 pt-20 pb-14">

    <div class="rule-centre text-bone/40 mb-16">
      <svg width="120" height="8" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#diamond-ornament"/></svg>
    </div>

    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-12 gap-14 sm:gap-10">
      <div class="sm:col-span-5">
        <a href="/" class="block mb-5">
          <span class="display text-3xl tracking-wider">better<span class="display-italic text-sage-soft">·</span>out</span>
          <div class="label-wide text-bone/50 mt-1 text-[0.6rem]">Coffee · Cape Town · MMXXVI</div>
        </a>
        <p class="font-serif italic text-bone/70 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-md mt-6">
          The first mould-free, lab-tested coffee enema in South Africa — and a quiet library of guides on living well from the inside out.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="sm:col-span-3">
        <div class="label-wide text-bone/45 mb-5">The Library</div>
        <ul class="space-y-2.5 font-serif text-bone/85">
          <li><a href="/guides/" class="hover:text-bone transition-colors">All five guides</a></li>
          <li><a href="/guides/steady/" class="hover:text-bone transition-colors">I — Steady</a></li>
          <li><a href="/guides/kitchen-apothecary/" class="hover:text-bone transition-colors">II — The Kitchen Apothecary</a></li>
          <li><a href="/guides/low-tox-living/" class="hover:text-bone transition-colors">III — Low-Tox Living</a></li>
          <li><a href="/guides/nourished-littles/" class="hover:text-bone transition-colors">IV — Nourished Littles</a></li>
          <li><a href="/guides/roots/" class="hover:text-bone transition-colors">V — Roots</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="sm:col-span-4">
        <div class="label-wide text-bone/45 mb-5">Correspondence</div>
        <ul class="space-y-2.5 font-serif text-bone/85">
          <li>
            <a href="https://instagram.com/better.out.co" rel="me noopener" target="_blank" class="hover:text-bone transition-colors">@better.out.co</a>
            <span class="text-bone/40 ml-2 text-sm italic">— on Instagram</span>
          </li>
          <li><a href="/about/" class="hover:text-bone transition-colors">A note from the founder</a></li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-8 font-serif italic text-bone/55 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-xs">
          The shop opens by appointment in late 2026. Until then, the library is open.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="rule-fine mt-16 mb-7" style="background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-bone) 18%, transparent);"></div>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between gap-4 label-wide text-bone/45">
      <div>© {year} Better Out Co. — Cape Town</div>
      <div class="text-bone/35">
        <!-- TODO: replace with CIPC registration number + registered address -->
        Reg. no. <span class="opacity-75">[pending]</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-7 text-xs font-sans font-light text-bone/45 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
      The information shared on this site and in our guides is educational. It is not medical advice and is not a substitute for the care of a qualified health professional. Please consult your doctor before changing your diet, beginning a cleansing protocol, or starting any new wellness practice — especially if you are pregnant, breastfeeding, a child, frail, or taking medication.
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>
